          },
          "reviewBody": "Honestly, My daughter started her studying in this school at her 3rd grade and now she is 8th. I am really happy that she is in this school. In my opinion in this school the studens doesn't mug up anything they just understand and let it out I realized this thing for my daughter. This is a worthy school. A great thanks to akshayah school",
